desc:
Sets the Lua module search path used by scripts specified by set_by_lua,
content_by_lua and others. The path string is in standard Lua path form, and ;;
can be used to stand for the original search paths.

notes:
Sets the Lua module search path used by scripts specified by set_by_lua,
